{"tid":1660093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國與歐盟達成脫歐協議 ?","createTime":"2019-10-17T10:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T11:54:13.000Z","uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6accf20f09f189d177df76e698e6c2c6b1cffa08","tid":1660093,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"歐盟委員會主席容克(Jean-Claude Juncker)於Twitter表示已達成脫歐協議，認為協議對歐盟及英國都是公平、平衡的，並建議歐洲理事會(EUCO)為協議「背書」。<br />\n<br />\n而英國首相約翰遜亦在Twitter表示，已達成新的協議且取回控制，並促請國會通過協議，讓政府可以處理其他重要議題如生活成本、醫療、罪惡及環境等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.970976/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.970976%2F2&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=1fe02c50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.970976/2</a>"},{"pid":"7e76622ef2f0a599c3383e474de596550c8426b8","tid":1660093,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ef7f96676d9be8d088178fc2e2251bfd75347aa3","tid":1660093,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:06:41.000Z","msg":"New Brexit deal agreed, says Boris Johnson<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nA Brexit deal has been agreed between UK and EU negotiating teams before a meeting of European leaders in Brussels.<br />\n<br />\nPrime Minister Boris Johnson tweeted: &quot;We've got a great new deal that takes back control.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe two sides have been working on the legal text of a deal, but it will still need the approval of both the UK and European parliaments.<br />\n<br />\nThe DUP has cast doubt on its sign off, saying they still cannot support it.<br />\n<br />\nThe Northern Irish party earlier released a statement saying they could not back proposals &quot;as things stand&quot;, and - after the PM's announcement - said their statement &quot;still stands&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nBut European Commission President Jean-Claude Juncker said it was a &quot;fair and balanced agreement&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nBoth he and Mr Johnson have urged their respective parliaments to back the deal. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-50079385?ns_linkname=news_central&amp;ns_mchannel=social&amp;ns_campaign=bbc_breaking&amp;ns_source=twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-50079385%3Fns_linkname%3Dnews_central%26ns_mchannel%3Dsocial%26ns_campaign%3Dbbc_breaking%26ns_source%3Dtwitter&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=c9641c00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-50079385%3Fns_linkname%3Dnews_central%26ns_mchannel%3Dsocial%26ns_campaign%3Dbbc_breaking%26ns_source%3Dtwitter&h=87c964f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-50079385?ns_linkname=news_central&amp;ns_mchannel=social&amp;ns_campaign=bbc_breaking&amp;ns_source=twitter</a>"},{"pid":"57d6daf8652ad6917b158f010cafa824da31d7d9","tid":1660093,"uid":50513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5BT4v0f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5BT4v0f.png&h=beab7723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好難捉摸呀"},{"pid":"a0894ae647ab3cff0a214ea1a5857d4d9b3dfecb","tid":1660093,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:18:21.000Z","msg":"又step back<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd296c9740d07750ce8025514e62494590e44a27","tid":1660093,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:19:49.000Z","msg":"DUP肯咩呢個方案"},{"pid":"4d4319b95e59c1991a